\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204400/extras/7ec49f052aa5eca04915eea3880e6945.avif?t=1749239781\" width=600 height=141 /></span><br><br><strong>Best played with a Gamepad!</strong>  Navigate through randomly generated mazes, break through walls, and boost your way around corners to secure your victory in a free-for-all battle with your friends!  One shot, you die.  Be the last one standing and abuse the power of screen-peeking to your heart's content.  Speed through the map using your boost power, break through walls using your shots, or simply take it tactical and utilize the windows and one-way pathways to your advantage;  You play your way.",
